topics.script:
play('"Oh dear, yes you must be a bit confused. When I first woke up in the mansion, I was so very afraid. Well, at least I think I was. That was so long ago, it\'s hard to remember. Memories tend to get little blurry in this place. Archie says it\u2019s all a part of the Master\u2019s work... All I know is this is his home, and I learned a long time ago to just enjoy what the Master\u2019s given us. You will too. In time."', 'dnulcpmnbb','maid');
makeUnbroachable('maid', 'this place');
